name: The first $1 paper money
description: The very first small size issued $1 bill (1928). Signatures of Harold Theodore Tate and Andrew W. Mellon.

name: Gangaroo #159
description: Gangaroos is a ground-breaking custom minting NFT project. 3600 Gangaroos minted on the Ethereum blockchain, with over 450 traits to choose from! Get your Gangaroo at https://gangaroos.com. Make the Gangaroo you love!

asset_contract.name: Gangaroos
asset_contract.description:
Gangaroos are the first fully customizable NFT. 3600 Gangaroos minted on the Ethereum blockchain, with over 450 unique traits to choose from! Get your Gangaroo at https://gangaroos.com

Key Project Features

* Customizable minting, first of its kind. Over 450 traits for you to hand pick from to help craft your custom NFT.

* Full commercial ownership for your Gangaroo NFT design (Customized or Traditional)
Community wallet.

* After sellout 100% of secondary sale royalties will be going to the community wallet for eternity!
Profit sharing from the revenue of any Gangaroos branded merchandise which will go to the community wallet

* The distribution of the funds in the community wallet will be voted on by the Gangaroos token holders

* All Gangaroos token holders will vote on proposed ideas & features that will create our 2.0 Roadmap.

* Every Gangaroo minted will be unique with no two being the exact same (Customized or Traditional).
